o place in our Constitution, no parallel courts, no creeping takeover!\n\nYour", "parentTweet": false, "likes": 3061}}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "text", "uuid": "1ASG4uxynz", "is_twitter": false, "is_admin": false, "score": 26, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8465213, "raw_content": ".", "author": "here2red", "created": 1772632413174, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "Scot", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "", "removal_source": "", "link": "", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "Now Jasmine Crockett and MTG can spend time consoling each other. LOL", "last_comment_created": 1772637097745, "content": "<p>.</p>\n", "score_down": 2, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 3, "score_up": 28, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"status": 200}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "text", "uuid": "1ASG4uyWyH", "is_twitter": false, "is_admin": false, "score": 18, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8465429, "raw_content": "I'm just pasting a message I sent to a friend. But it's what just happened.\nWho can I call and speak to to report this shit to?????\nI just called the VA and the main fiduciary hub that handles payments to disabled vets. The VA rep had a very strong Hong Kong accent, impatient and just wanted to get it done, but did do his job. Then connected me to the main fiduciary center. Indian accent guy. Also impatient but answered all my questions the same. Both were given his full name, DOB, military branch and SSN.\nThe Indian guy then thought he hung up but hadn't! I sat there listening for almost 10 minutes while he ate....snorted, clanged his dishes, chewed, swallowed.....I could hear it all! Imagining what kind of curry he was having.\nThen at the end a sudden ..... \"Oh!\" And he hung up.\nObviously an at home call worker , probably in another country and getting such information and giving me feedback from government data he's looking up on his computer!\nWTF!\nWho can I trust to call to report or complain to???\nThis is crazy. My veteran brother died and I'm reporting in to foreigners!!!! To make sure everything is being done correctly with the fudituary who was giving his widow attitude when she inquired as to what to do next. Maybe the fudituary is also overseas?\n", "author": "USMC6541E5", "created": 1772639556933, "profile_picture": "8W4BNLRnoEkC", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "MrSteadFast1", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "", "removal_source": "", "link": "", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "I need advice. My disabled veteran brother died last week. I called VA and was answered by \"at home\" call workers eating. Hong Kong and Indian accents.", "last_comment_created": 1772641083098, "content": "<p>I'm just pasting a message I sent to a friend. But it's what just happened.\nWho can I call and speak to to report this shit to?????\nI just called the VA and the main fiduciary hub that handles payments to disabled vets. The VA rep had a very strong Hong Kong accent, impatient and just wanted to get it done, but did do his job. Then connected me to the main fiduciary center. Indian accent guy. Also impatient but answered all my questions the same. Both were given his full name, DOB, military branch and SSN.\nThe Indian guy then thought he hung up but hadn't! I sat there listening for almost 10 minutes while he ate....snorted, clanged his dishes, chewed, swallowed.....I could hear it all! Imagining what kind of curry he was having.\nThen at the end a sudden ..... &quot;Oh!&quot; And he hung up.\nObviously an at home call worker , probably in another country and getting such information and giving me feedback from government data he's looking up on his computer!\nWTF!\nWho can I trust to call to report or complain to???\nThis is crazy. My veteran brother died and I'm reporting in to foreigners!!!! To make sure everything is being done correctly with the fudituary who was giving his widow attitude when she inquired as to what to do next. Maybe the fudituary is also overseas?</p>\n", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 4, "score_up": 18, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"status": 200}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "2028877856541962497", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "link", "uuid": "1ASG4sgdrt", "is_twitter": true, "is_admin": false, "score": 902, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "geotus", "id": 8463049, "raw_content": "", "author": "CyanScales", "created": 1772562992787, "profile_picture": "1cOg4Zdci1jH", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "ActualStory", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "twitter.com", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "https://media.scored.co/preview/1ASG4sgdrt.png", "removal_source": "", "link": "https://twitter.com/i/status/2028877856541962497", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "\"Did Israel force your hand to launch these strikes against Iran?\"\r\n\r\nTru